name: Birch Bark Pendants & Earrings
description:
From the land of the silver birch, these pendants & earrings are truly Canadian!  Real birch bark collected from fallen birch trees is cleaned & bezel set under a mineral watch crystal like a gemstone.  Natural colour & pattern variations in the bark ensure that your birch bark jewellery will definitely be one of a kind. Product made to order.

Materials: sterling silver, birch bark, quartz crystal
Dimensions: 1.75cm wide x .5cm deep

I am happy to do custom orders, please contact me to order your birch bark jewellery in a different metal or with a different colour of bark.

Please note that while every effort has been made to make this resistant to moisture, they are still made from a natural biodegradable material and as such must not be immersed in water or cleaning liquids.
